lyrics:
[verse]
In neon streets, the battle cries ignite
Amidst the smoke, we're soldiers of the night
Synths pulsate, echoing the fight
Our hearts beat loud, daring dreams take flight

[chorus]
War of stars, on an electric tide we glide
Blade of hope, cutting through the darkest side
As we dance with shadows, guided by our pride
In this synthwave war, we won't be denied
